    dc:creator "Ho, Hsuan-Ching; Roberts, Clive D.; Shao, Kwang-Tsao" ;
    dc:date "2013" ;
    dc:title "Revision of batfishes (Lophiiformes: Ogcocephalidae) of New Zealand and adjacent waters, with description of two new species of the genus Malthopsis" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.216078>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.216079>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.216077> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.216078>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Malthopsis parva sp. nov., holotype, NMNZ P. 017180, 46.4 mm SL. A. dorsal view. B. lateral view. C. ventral view. D. drawing of dorsal view, illustrated by M. Freebone. E. CSIRO 6031 - 01, paratype, 51.2 mm, fresh, photo by CSIRO. A – C. photo by C. Struthers." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/216078/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.216079>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Malthopsis parva sp. nov., holotype. A. closed view of dorsal head. B. closed view of lateral head. C. closed view of left subopercular region. D. ventral view of disc showing the naked area and some flattened bucklers at pelvic fin base area. Photo by C. Struthers." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/216079/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.216077>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Distribution map of ogcocephalid species found in New Zealand waters. Square = Halieutaea stellata; star = Halieutopsis bathyoreos; triangle = Malthopsis asperata; cross = Malthopsis mitrigera; and circle = Malthopsis parva. One dot may represent more than one capture. Open dots indicate the holotype localities, including the holotype of H. maoria (open square)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/216077/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

